{"tid":1130200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15歲仔墮「執法人員」陷阱　變賣母25萬首飾交騙徒","createTime":"2019-04-29T01:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T01:23:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c86404432fdad5a5242176148d396c5f0ad55f4","tid":1130200,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/photo/bkn-20190429003737150-0429_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190429083429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190429%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190429003737150-0429_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190429083429&h=15dd5a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電騙黨又得逞！昨日(28日)晚上7時許，一名49歲女子在將軍澳廣明苑一單位報案，指失去一批首飾。警方接報到場調查，女事主15歲兒子指早前收到一名男子來電，對方自稱是內地執法人員，並指他涉及一宗刑事案件，少年按該名男子指示，將其母親約值25萬港元的首飾變賣，並將款項存入一內地戶口。 <br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由將軍澳警區刑事調查隊，暫未有人被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/bkn-20190429003737150-0429_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190429%2Fbkn-20190429003737150-0429_00822_001.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9cwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=bd264112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/bkn-20190429003737150-0429_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4beda6ed7c83766756a43ecaa62c50c3cffa3f94","tid":1130200,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6e958fd77f51c934a8508fa222c1d8f7caff6f","tid":1130200,"uid":4052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"好明顯個仔拎咗去用啦屌。"},{"pid":"7f3baf6088c4a821cc7aaef6a7f52eba91039253","tid":1130200,"uid":90166,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:23:58.000Z","msg":"偷老母錢扮俾人呃"}]}